Description: Brazilian Burst Keith Urban single cutaway for sale.  As new, not a scratch, dent, nor flaw and its been played regularly. Compared to the many beginner electric guitars on the market, the fit, finish, quality, playability and sound of Keith's brand is some of the best.  Best XMAS present ever for a newer player to grow with and affordable enough for them to figure out if guitar is their instrument of choice.  A very pretty, classic, single cutaway, done in a version of sunburst with 2 volume and tone controls for both humbucker pickups and a pickup switch to select each pickup or both.  That said, you can get any sound from the guitar you prefer - rhythm, rock leads, country strumming, loud and noisy, or quiet and sweet.  As new condition, played lightly, set up and sound is great for a beginner guitar.  This guitar even sounds great when not plugged in, not the case for most solid body electrics.  This is a guitar only auction and the package offered in other listings is not included - honestly the other stuff is not the quality of the guitar anyway.
Title: Keith Urban Ripcord Brazilian Burst 6-String Electric Guitar - Right-handed
